Source: vchord-bm25
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/tensorchord/VectorChord-bm25

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-vchord-bm25
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-vchord-bm25
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: BM25 ranking and indexing for PostgreSQL
 VectorChord-BM25 implements BM25 ranking and Block-Max WAND indexing inside
 PostgreSQL. It can be used alone with bm25vector values, or together with
 pg_tokenizer for customized text tokenization.
